Text: 'I visited to kasol last june oh! That place takes my heart what a beautiful
  place it is mountains rivers the combination is woh

  Weather is lit there are many places in it for roaming there is a sikh gurdwara
  called manikaran sahib peeps take hot water bath there nobody knows where the hot
  water comes from in that river peaceful place and many Israeli came there many foreigners
  came there they enjoy all this atmosphere, weather, culture, food etc.'
